      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellisburg%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Woodville, northwest of the village on Sandy Creek’s north branch, began as “Wood’s Settlement” after a pioneer family.",
